Morning, I'm trying to make checkboxes on the "subscription preferences" system template page easier to click. For some reason, I can't seem to select checkboxes/anything when viewing the actual page but I can in a preview. Here's the general code:
```{% require_js %}
  <script>
    window.addEventListener("load", (event) => {
      console.log("form ready here");
      // Select all elements with the class 'item'
      document.querySelectorAll(".item").forEach((item) => {
        console.log("item", item); // logs in preview, but not live
      });
    });
  </script>
{% end_require_js %} ```
